SENSATIONAL MODERN OFFICE SPACE ON PROSPECT ROAD – 125 SQM + AMPLE ON-SITE PARKING

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Formally occupied by Bank SA, 113 Prospect Road is an opportunity to take advantage of the surging Prospect precinct. 

A standalone offering of 358sqm, it has a flexible layout that an incoming tenant can easily adapt to suit. 

Afforded prominent signage opportunities and 12 on-site parks, it is an offering that won't last long. 

Lease Term: Negotiable
Options: Negotiable 
Rent Reviews: Negotiable 
Date Available: Immediately
